{{Quote|With this device, one Ewok can lift an entire cartload.|Logray|<ref name="The Three Lessons">{{Ewoks|The Three Lessons}}</ref>}}
A '''supply lift''' was a device developed by the [[Shaman/Legends|Shaman]] [[Logray/Legends|Logray]] on the [[Endor/Legends|Forest Moon of Endor]] to lift supplies of food from the forest floor up to the heights of [[Bright Tree Village/Legends|Bright Tree Village]]. The lift was essentially a platform with a pulley attached. The device first came into use during the [[stranglethorn crisis]] where it was destroyed by a rampaging [[stranglethorn]].

